\name{depgraph-package}
\alias{depgraph-package}
\alias{depgraph}
\title{depgraph: Dataset Dependency Knowledge Graphs for Leakage-Aware Machine Learning}
\description{
The \pkg{depgraph} package provides typed graph objects for representing
dataset structure, sample provenance, and leakage-relevant dependencies in
biomedical machine learning workflows.
}
\details{
Version 1 is focused on dataset dependency graphs rather than biological
interaction networks. The package is designed to complement the
\pkg{bioLeak} ecosystem by exposing explicit graph-derived constraints that
can later be used for leakage-aware splitting and evaluation.
}
\docType{package}

